description: The Chicago Tribune editorial board defended Caitlin Clark in the wake of the hometown team causing controversy when Chennedy Carter fouled the Indiana Fever rookie.
title: Chicago Tribune editorial board defends Caitlin Clark, likens Sky guard's hip-check to assault

description: Washington Post publisher William Lewis offered a grim assessment of the state of the paper during a staff meeting following the ousting of its executive editor.
title: WaPo boss sounds alarm over dwindling audience in heated staff meeting: 'People are not reading your stuff'

description: "The Dukes of Hazzard" star John Schneider has unveiled his girlfriend just over a year after his wife died from breast cancer. Alicia Allain Schneider was 53 when she died in February 2023.
title: 'Dukes of Hazzard' star John Schneider finds love a year after wife's death: 'God sent a widower to a widow'

description: Dallas Cowboys legend Emmitt Smith couldn't hold back his tears in a video he posted on Instagram after learning of former teammate Larry Allen's death.
title: Emmitt Smith fights back tears after learning Cowboys teammate Larry Allen died: 'My heart is just broken'

description: Chicago Sky rookie Angel Reese said Monday she has no problem with being the villain and wanted fans to realize that she's also the reason why women's basketball is so popular.
title: Sky's Angel Reese willing to play 'bad guy role' as more eyes turn to women's basketball

description: Now-former California state Assemblyman Vince Fong, a Republican, has been sworn into Congress to complete former Speaker Kevin McCarthy's term.
title: Republican Vince Fong sworn into Kevin McCarthy's old House seat

description: Louisiana state lawmakers on Monday approved a tough new law that could allow judges to order convicted child molesters to undergo surgical castration.
title: Louisiana lawmakers approve law that would allow surgical castration of convicted child molesters

description: A Nebraska woman was discovered to be alive Monday after she was pronounced dead and transported to a funeral home, authorities said.
title: Woman believed dead found alive at Nebraska funeral home
